title: Controversial cake served as inter-Korean summit ends
text:
Controversial cake served as inter-Korean summit ends 4:59pm BST - 00:31
A controversial cake with a map of the Korean peninsula and islands claimed by both Seoul and Tokyo was unveiled at the inter-Korea summit. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
